---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Who writes lateston.ai, the three-section format, and what each action tag means."
>
  <article class="prose-body">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About</h1>

    <p>
      My name is <a
        href="https://github.com/hassanhabib"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">Hassan Habib</a
      >. I am a software engineer. I read more AI news than I should, and I
      built lateston.ai to give that reading a single, predictable shape.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The three-section format</h2>

    <p>
      Every review on this site has the same three sections, in the same order. The sections
      are numbered so you can scan them without reading them.
    </p>

    <ol start="0">
      <li><strong>Signal and Analysis.</strong> What happened and what the thing actually is once you remove the marketing.</li>
      <li><strong>Testing and the Standard opinion.</strong> How to verify the claim yourself and the framework view.</li>
      <li><strong>What to do with this.</strong> Concrete guidance on what is next.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The three actions</h2>

    <p>
      Every review ends with exactly one action. The action is the point of the review.
    </p>

    <ol start="0">
      <li><strong>Learn it.</strong> Understand this. It matters and you need the context.</li>
      <li><strong>Take it.</strong> Use this now. It is ready and it pays off.</li>
      <li><strong>Leave it.</strong> Skip this. The cost is higher than the benefit.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The framework</h2>

    <p>
      Reviews on this site are framed by <a
        href="https://github.com/hassanhabib/The-Standard"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">The Standard</a
      > and the Tri-Nature AI Agent Framework.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
